      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的流程图，核心是从入口控制器到工作节点的流转。起点是Infra_IngressController，它要连到一个判断节点Infra_WorkerNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，IngressController作为起始节点。这个Infra_WorkerNode是菱形判断框对吧？它分支出去的两个路径分别是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，是判断节点。如果WorkerNode状态正常，走Yes分支到Infra_RedisCache；如果不正常，走No分支到Infra_EtcdCluster做修复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：IngressController指向WorkerNode判断框，然后分出Yes到RedisCache，No到EtcdCluster。两个分支标签我也标上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，EtcdCluster修复完之后需要有个循环，要回到WorkerNode重新判断，直到状态正常为止。这个闭环很重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，EtcdCluster画了一条回指线到WorkerNode，形成循环结构。这样修复后可以重新检测节点状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "RedisCache之后还需要再连到一个最终的WorkerNode，表示缓存就绪后真正进入工作节点处理。这是最后一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：RedisCache指向的是一个新的WorkerNode节点，还是回到前面那个判断节点？从语义上看应该是新的终点节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
